{"title":"天晴了","authors":["孟昭林"],"dates":[{"year":1947,"month":9,"day":14}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"天晴了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孟昭林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（滦正获北营村街头诗）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（一）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天晴了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨停了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地主变成狗熊了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天亮了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"变样了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穷人起来算帐了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（二）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子孩子好好睡，妈"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈今天去开会；开会"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干什吗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斗争大恶霸；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"讲讲理，出出气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要回咱那房子地；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻翻身，抬抬头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给你爹爹报报仇。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}